    Hazardous Waste Facilities

     * Hazardous Waste Management Project Documents  DTSC posts on its web
       site key documents related to entities that manage hazardous waste.
       Click on the link for web-available information on entities that
       handle hazardous waste (generators; transporters; facilities
       permitted with Resource Conservation and Recovery (RCRA) permits or
       standardized permits; and other authorizations and notifications).
       If you can't find the facility or other entity that you're looking
       for, call our Public and Business Liaisons at 800-728-6942, or
       800-72TOXIC. They can direct you to a Public Participation
       Specialist or suggest where you might find more information.
